{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/keyframes-name-pattern/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/function-url-scheme-whitelist/","description":"function-whitelist 指定允许的函数的白名单。 选项 array|string: \\[\"array\", \"of\", \"unprefixed\", /functions/ or \"regex\"]|\"function\"|\"/regex/\" 如果字符串用 \"/\"…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"function-whitelist\"><a href=\"#function-whitelist\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>function-whitelist</h1>\n<p>指定允许的函数的白名单。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">transform</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">scale</span>(1); }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**            ↑\n * 这个函数 */</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>array|string</code>: <code>[\"array\", \"of\", \"unprefixed\", /functions/ or \"regex\"]|\"function\"|\"/regex/\"</code></p>\n<p>如果字符串用 <code>\"/\"</code> 包围（例如 <code>\"/^rgb/\"</code>），则将其解释为正则表达式。</p>\n<p>给定：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\">[<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"scale\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"rgba\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"linear-gradient\"</span>]</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">transform</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">rotate</span>(1); }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hsla</span>(170, 50%, 45%, 1)\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>:\n    red,\n    <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">-webkit-radial-gradient</span>(red, green, blue);\n}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: red; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">transform</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">scale</span>(1); }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">rgba</span>(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>:\n    red,\n    <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">-moz-linear-gradient</span>(45deg, blue, red);\n}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/function-whitelist.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/function-whitelist/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/function-whitelist/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/function-whitelist/index.html.443a6960454cc53d37de38ff8abe2f1d.json"}